ven by the added mass term. The\nresults of this paper are of particular interest for engineers who need to grab\nthe essential features associated to the vibration of a solid body in a still\nfluid.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 May 2017 11:00:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-27"}
