hase separation between metallic and ferromagnetic chains in a\nnon-metallic matrix may be crucial for CMR.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 May 2017 15:19:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 5 May 2017 16:47:12 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 22 Feb 2019 12:17:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-19"}
